Easy Scheduler is a distributed workflow task scheduling system that mainly solves the intricate dependencies of data development ETL, but cannot intuitively monitor the health status of tasks. Easy Scheduler assembles tasks in a DAG manner, and can monitor the running state for tasks in time, at the same time, support retry, recover failure from specified nodes, suspend and kill tasks, etc. Easy Scheduler is developed by many partners who have worked in workflow scheduling for many years, and is committed to become the mainstay of big data platform, making scheduling It has become easier, and we can see our original intention from its Chinese name “易调度”. If you are not satisfied with the current scheduling on the market, welcome to use easy scheduler. Welcome everyone to join in